#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:2
msgid "gVisor installation"
msgstr "gVisor 安裝"

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:4
msgid ""
"You can mostly get by just following installation instructions in the "
"`gVisor Docker Quick Start`_ guide."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:7
msgid ""
"There are a few caveats to installation, which likely depend on your local "
"environment. For ``systemd`` based OS, you do need to configure the Docker "
"daemon to avoid systemd cgroups."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:13
msgid "Arch"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:15
msgid "Follow the installation and quick start directions like normal:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:17
msgid ""
"% yay -S gvisor-bin\n"
"...\n"
"% sudo runsc install"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:23
msgid ""
"You do need to instruct Docker to avoid systemd cgroups. You will need to "
"make further changes to ``/etc/docker/daemon.json`` and restart the Docker "
"service:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:27
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \"runtimes\": {\n"
"        \"runsc\": {\n"
"            \"path\": \"/usr/bin/runsc\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"exec-opts\": [\"native.cgroupdriver=cgroupfs\"]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:38
msgid "Fedora"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:40
msgid ""
"Install docker from their repositories, the one included in Fedora doesn't "
"work, using their `convenience script`_ is an easy way to do it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:43
msgid "`Install gvisor manually`_, the one included in Fedora doesn't work."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:44
msgid "Enable cgroups v1:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:46
msgid ""
"% sudo grubby --update-kernel=ALL --args=\"systemd."
"unified_cgroup_hierarchy=0\""
msgstr ""
"% sudo grubby --update-kernel=ALL --args=\"systemd."
"unified_cgroup_hierarchy=0\""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:53
msgid ""
"Docker is correctly configured when you can run this command from the quick "
"start guide:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/gvisor.rst:56
msgid ""
"% docker run --rm -ti --runtime=runsc readthedocs/build dmesg\n"
"[    0.000000] Starting gVisor...\n"
"..."
msgstr ""
"% docker run --rm -ti --runtime=runsc readthedocs/build dmesg\n"
